Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.95,0:02:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真熱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,的說～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,下個禮拜暑假就開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,想和大家一起去哪裡玩玩欸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好呀好呀 去海邊吧海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.81,0:02:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,咦～山裡更好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,接詞遊戲～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.78,0:02:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,夏天想去的地方的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.89,0:02:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.38,0:02:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.89,0:02:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是山裡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}山～裡～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你這個死頑固
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個都別吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,兩者綜合一下 就在家裡待著如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你那是綜合哪兩者啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我的話 只要是涼快的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,只要和大家一起 去哪都很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,咦～去海邊嘛 海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,麥啦 會曬傷欸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,陽子穿泳衣很合適的樣子 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:03:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 我話先說在前面 我只能算是普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你那個算普通的話 那我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}你很難搞欸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,海邊我之前去過囉 夏威夷哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 藍色的天空 白色的雲彩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,很開心的樣子～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.87,0:03:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一看是星期六 就飛過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我的個子明明就更高的說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,塞個胸墊進去不就萬事OK了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 快吐槽我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼帶這個來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,決定不下來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.02,0:03:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,現在到底是在說什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那就這樣吧 用撲克來決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,輸者要聽贏者的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,山裡更好～山裡更好～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法呢 那就去山裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,富士山我來啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那到是有點難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真熱 沒有忘記的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 水壺 漁具 防蟲劑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,泳衣乖乖放在家裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,讓大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我勒 忍 你不熱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那怎麼看都不是去爬山穿的衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是Cosplay嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,森林裡的妖精哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呢 你大腦沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,森林系女孩！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼不是登山系女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,森女比較可愛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,忍很可愛哦 就像妖精一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想見到痛苦萬分的妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,女孩子為了美 必須要學會忍耐才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,這是姐姐告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好熱～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 但你可別倒下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,話說可憐還真慢欸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是和她爸爸一起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.25,0:05:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這什麼這什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好囉 大家都上車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你是何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,大小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,暑假 雖然不是富士山 但是去登山了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是山欸！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:05:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,防曬乳都快被汗燙融了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,氣喘不過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在吃關東煮之類的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不是會「呼——呼——」這樣吹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.82,0:06:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此 讓空氣冷下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好慢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,快到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,爬到山頂以後就會有種令人滿意的達成感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 不是那邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 這裡可以享受河釣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸把東西都準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這才是主要目的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,釣魚就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,想當初在英國的時候可是被某人百般調教呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,調教？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,釣到的魚就是午餐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,能釣到大的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.57,0:07:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,得讓忍看到我帥氣的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不會輸給可憐的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲 好熱…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,\上鉤囉/
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,釣到大傢伙囉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可憐好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,小時候就很擅長釣魚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,等等哦 忍 我馬上就為你抓來好吃的魚！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,有這份心就夠了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.52,0:07:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動囉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃呢 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我為大家做了便當哦 可以的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,哇——
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,萬歲～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹嘛啦 有稍微進步一點的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真的欸！好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真想讓綾成為我的那個呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.10,0:08:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 是什麼啦>///<
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,有母親的味道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好多蟲子喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.87,0:08:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,忍 危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.22,0:08:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起…蚊子…蚊子…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:09:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,綾！求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我如果和綾一起的話 感覺什麼都能做得到！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 你突然間是在說什麼呢>///<
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.89,0:09:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所以一起去跳水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,辦不到的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,如果有帶泳衣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你就真的那麼想游泳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,就來玩玩水忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.46,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣才是青春嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好涼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,綾 快來 很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你居然潑我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,潑囉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那就稍微玩一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,忍 發現螃蟹了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,螃蟹先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,忍！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.34,0:10:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你又來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,看我這一招如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這是犯規
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.95,0:10:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,綾 快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,忍——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,忍——！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,吸飽了水 衣服變得非常重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,忍 沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.84,0:10:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係啦 反正是夏天 很快就會乾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.93,0:11:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但是髒掉的衣服恢復不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,還不都是因為你穿這種衣服來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就算沒有這件衣服 忍還是妖精 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之後 我們釣到了非常多的魚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,忍吃著我烤的魚 說非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,下次想去爬看看富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,治癒人心呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,忍 你什麼時候來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲 可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.08,0:11:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 她們兩個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,她們兩個……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你掉入湖裡的 是金色的愛麗絲嗎 還是金色的可憐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我無法做抉擇 非常難選啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這什麼鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…金髮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.84,0:12:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,忍真的很喜歡金髮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這種的如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有好多種顏色的頭髮喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,藍色的頭髮好像也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.32,0:12:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以 忍別染上奇怪的色癖啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我以前穿過的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好 穿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.95,0:12:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 忍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可憐也有帶過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,YES
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:13:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是第一次參加日本的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.29,0:13:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,大家會一起拉載著超大武士的花車對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,花車？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,味噌？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,呀——呀——咄！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那是青森的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,今天要去的是本地的夏日祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那大文字跟神與歸社呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,大概沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲 握住這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼關係 有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,呀 惡代官大人～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}金髮加上浴衣也是別有一番風味
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,忍要穿什麼去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我要穿…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,陽子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,浴衣很適合喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是因為黑髮的關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.81,0:14:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,陽子的也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}久等囉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這是邪門外道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,燈籠！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,鳥居！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,法披！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy的時候就穿法披哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,又在亂說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥——
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,烏丸老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.00,0:14:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啦 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,小烏迷路了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,跟哥哥走散了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不 當然是只有我一個人來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不過有3支欸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.14,0:14:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,會胖的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,要先去哪個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,先吃燒餅？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:14:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,炒麵或許也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,棉花糖則是甜點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,巧克力香蕉也是甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真讓人猶豫欸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.89,0:15:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那就先快速地把想吃 想玩的東西先確認一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 我已經想要先吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子吃撐的時候再說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,「啊 我好想再吃這個」或是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,「零錢不夠用了」可就晚囉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.09,0:15:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這是常有的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,得仔細想要吃什麼才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.70,0:15:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,章魚燒很好吃的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,已經開始吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 老闆兒 來一份章魚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…300元
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好 300元對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲不買嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,要來一個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,很燙的 小心一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你早點說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼就重新來過 出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.18,0:16:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,GO GO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你還是照一下鏡子比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.96,0:16:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.47,0:16:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,玩得真瘋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,來決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真熟練啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,既然這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,掰掰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,難得撈到的說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是Catch and release哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我也完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.34,0:17:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,艾菲爾鐵塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 火災嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,祭典的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也想加入
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下 可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,陽子也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,綾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我在這邊看就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,綾你該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}陽子 阿綾綾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊應該是只有打太鼓的人才能上去的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真自由啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎麼跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好開心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來就是煙火了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼時候放煙火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,咚 咚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,蠻可惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟不是煙火大會嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,煙火 煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.90,0:18:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,有的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,有煙火嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然比不上衝天炮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,別亂揮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,綾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.96,0:19:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不去放煙火嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,從什麼時候開始覺得痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,在車站等你們的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那不就是一開始嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼不說出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不想給大家潑冷水嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,放著不管才會這麼痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,下次要好好說出來唷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}真好啊 沖天炮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,勇姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,勇姐也來玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,勇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.93,0:19:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你買了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.36,0:19:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,西瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛大家一起逛廟會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這是給姐姐的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,大概沒辦法全吃光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,忍 謝謝你帶我來廟會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,超開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這也是我最開心的一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,和別的時候有什麼不同嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 真要說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.33,0:20:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那大概就是有愛麗絲一起逛的關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,忍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,燒完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,夏天也快結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,還有很多很多煙火哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 高射砲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,別放喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那種的要到更廣闊的地方才能放
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 都已經點上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,別對著這邊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,快避難！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎麼辦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.37,0:21:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,澆水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,別往我這邊來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.94,0:22:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那個少女在晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.95,0:22:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,獨自一個人對著桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.23,0:22:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在寂靜的房間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.05,0:22:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,咕嘰 咕嘰 咕嘰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.95,0:22:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,只有時鐘發出陰森恐怖的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.20,0:23:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,咕嘰 咕嘰 咕嘰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.26,0:23:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.61,0:23:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,凌晨0點 9月1號
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.93,0:23:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,暑假作業完全沒寫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,別一副事不關己的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.96,0:23:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,都已經8月31號了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.80,0:23:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,用俳句來說出夏天的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.29,0:23:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.32,0:23:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,登山和廟會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是小忍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,放煙火時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,可憐很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.79,0:23:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是小忍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.90,0:23:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,也不用非得要讓我出場的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.18,0:23:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,See you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
